data.description: PRICE IMPROVEMENT! Welcome to this stunning three-bedroom, two-bathroom house built in 2022, located in the beautiful Villages at Avalon community. This place has it all! With low HOA fees of only $189 a quarter, you'll have access to the clubhouse, fitness center, playground, and pool. Step inside and admire the ceramic tile flooring throughout, with cozy carpet in the bedrooms. The modern kitchen is a chef's dream, featuring stainless steel GE appliances and gorgeous granite countertops in both the kitchen and bathrooms. The spacious open floor plan is perfect for entertaining, and you'll love the convenience of the master bedroom located in the rear, complete with a large, spacious walk-in closet. The backyard is spacious perfect for hosting family & friends. Don't miss out on this incredible opportunity to call this house your home!
